# User Data Deletion Instructions – Reliance CATV & Entertainment Services

Effective Date: May 11, 2026

If you wish to request deletion of your personal data collected by Reliance CATV & Entertainment Services through our Facebook Page, Messenger chatbot, or Facebook App integration, please follow the instructions below.

## How to Request Data Deletion

You may request deletion of your data by contacting our support team through any of the following methods:

### Facebook Page

Send a direct message to:
Reliance CATV & Entertainment Services Facebook Page

### Email Request

Email us with the subject:
“User Data Deletion Request”

Include the following details:

* Full Name
* Facebook Name/Profile
* Account ID (if applicable)
* Contact Number
* Reason for deletion request

## What Data Will Be Deleted

Upon verification, we may delete:

* Messenger conversation records
* Contact information
* Facebook-related user information
* Service inquiry history
* Other stored personal information not required by law or active service agreements

## Processing Time

Data deletion requests are typically processed within 7–30 business days depending on the nature of the request and verification process.

## Important Note

Some information may be retained if required for:

* Legal obligations
* Billing and financial records
* Fraud prevention
* Active service accounts or unresolved disputes

